Additional Terms for Research and Academic Use:

This software and associated research artifacts — including datasets, annotation
guidelines, model configurations, and evaluation scripts — were developed as part
of an undergraduate thesis at Universitas Diponegoro. Users of this software must:

1. Cite the original research appropriately in any academic work, publication,
   or derivative project that makes use of this codebase, dataset, or methodology.

2. Use the annotated dataset solely for research, educational, or non-commercial
   purposes. Commercial use of the dataset requires explicit written permission
   from the author.

3. Respect the privacy of the original review authors. The dataset must not be
   used in any manner that could facilitate re-identification of individual users
   or any form of targeted profiling.

4. Ensure that any deployed system built upon this codebase complies with
   applicable data protection regulations, including but not limited to
   Indonesia's Personal Data Protection Law (UU PDP No. 27 Tahun 2022).

5. Acknowledge that model performance metrics reported in this repository reflect
   results on a specific domain and dataset. Users are responsible for validating
   performance in their own deployment context before relying on the system
   for any consequential decision-making.

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any
misuse, inaccurate predictions, or downstream harm resulting from improper
implementation, out-of-domain deployment, or failure to validate the system
in a target environment.

For questions regarding academic use, dataset access, or collaboration,
please contact the author directly via the channels listed below.

